Many women suffer with discomfort due to elongated labia caused by age, childbirth, or genetics. 𝑳𝒂𝒃𝒊𝒂𝒑𝒍𝒂𝒔𝒕𝒚 is the surgical reduction or reshaping of the inner vaginal lips. 

𝐁𝐄𝐍𝐄𝐅𝐈𝐓𝐒 𝐨𝐟 𝐋𝐚𝐛𝐢𝐚𝐩𝐥𝐚𝐬𝐭𝐲
-Reduces enlarged labia & reshapes irregular labia
-Restores & rejuvenates for a youthful appearance
-Restore even skin tone
-Resolve cosmetic concerns such as “camel toe”
-Improve discomfort and functionality
-Minimally invasive, outpatient procedure
-Local anesthesia
-Customize your results
-30 – 60 minute procedure
-Minimal downtime and quick recovery

Do you want a 𝗖𝗢𝗡𝗦𝗨𝗟𝗧𝗔𝗧𝗜𝗢𝗡? 👇🏽
